            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> beef bolognese</strong> over the<strong> fresh tagliatelle</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> and <strong>chopped parsley </strong>and enjoy!</p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Loved this recipe? Keep an eye out for it on the Everyday Favourites section of our menu.</span></strong></p>",
